Actions.Text: ----------------------------------------------------------------# Auth: Christopher Stone# dCre: 2018/12/03 14:46# dMod: 2018/12/03 14:47# Appl: Finder# Task: Move items in the User's Downloads Folder to the Trash.# Libs: None# Osax: None# Tags: @Applescript, @Script, @Finder, @Move, @Items, @User, @Downloads, @Folder, @Trash----------------------------------------------------------------set downloadsFolder to path to downloads foldertell application "Finder"	delete (items of downloadsFolder as alias list)end tell----------------------------------------------------------------
